 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lashinda_Demus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lashinda_Demus\"}, {\"begin\": 870, \"end\": 878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9838965606201466, \"rank\": 0.016362875343175355, \"text\": \"Republic\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver medal spot\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carter toldJamaica Observerthat she spent much of the last few years in regret, as a career that at one time looked destined to deliver multiple major championship medals seemed destined to end without that elusive World Championships or Olympics piece of jewellery.\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 1200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toldJamaica\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few years\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"regret\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"a career\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"one time\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple major championship medals\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"that elusive World Championships or Olympics piece\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"jewellery\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am elated!\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not the way I expected or wanted it to be but it's still an achievement that I am super grateful for.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"an achievement\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am now a bronze medallist, and that will be with me my entire life.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bronze medallist\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"my entire life\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My child will be able to say that my mommy is a bronze medallist and I am just grateful, regardless,\\\" Carter said.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9950010684583732, \"rank\": 0.005015985002349619, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My child\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"my mommy\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medallist\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What I have taken from this?\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just persevere, never give up.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[Through] determination and hard work, no matter what, things will come through,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"determination\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former World Junior champion had developed a reputation for underperforming at major events, not being able to back up her remarkable performance on the Diamond League circuit - which reaped four Diamond trophies, with global podium finishes.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1823, \"end\": 1837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999053779406113, \"rank\