Jamaica Olympic Association - during a special ceremony at the foot of the Eiffel Tower during the Paris 2024 Olympic Games, has changed her perspective on her time on the track.\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2132, \"end\": 2138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9950010684583732, \"rank\": 0.005015985002349619, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}, {\"begin\": 2179, \"end\": 2185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999998695848348, \"rank\": 1.2955066387372578e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 2275, \"end\": 2302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamaica Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Olympic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the emotions\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"that evening\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2213}, {\"ngram\": \"thanks\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"the efforts\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2271}, {\"ngram\": \"a special ceremony\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2330}, {\"ngram\": \"the foot\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2342}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2398}, {\"ngram\": \"her perspective\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"her time\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was actually in great shape at first, and then I think I got injured, and then the championships came.\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great shape\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"the championships\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My heat wasn't so good, my semi wasn't so great either, but then I pulled it together in the final and, gratefully, I got fourth - and because of what happened I eventually got the bronze medal.\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My heat\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Crossing the line, I was very disappointed because I was one of the best during the season, and had been for a few years, but I just wasn't able to get that medal so it was a really sad moment for me, because I had been called: 'The girl who always finished fourth'.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 3024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2775}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2848}, {\"ngram\": \"a few years\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2878}, {\"ngram\": \"that medal\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"a really sad moment\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"The girl\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 2995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was branded 'Kaliese Fourth' so just the fact that I am getting that bronze medal now, I am really happy,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"'Kaliese Fourth\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3054}, {\"ngram\": \"that bronze medal\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had medals but this is the one I wanted.\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3164}, {\"ngram\": \"the one\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not the colour I wanted it to be but I am grateful that I can hang up my spikes and now know that I am not only an Olympian but also a medallist, and I am very grateful for that,\\\" said Carter.\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3315, \"end\": 3323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.925860601467261e-12, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3385, \"end\": 3391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9950010684583732, \"rank\": 0.005015985002349619, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the colour\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3214}, {\"ngram\": \"my spikes\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3279}, {\"ngram\": \"a medallist\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking ahead to the reallocation ceremony which is set for August 9, Carter says she is excited to be sharing the occasion with her family.\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3464, \"end\": 3470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9950010684583732, \"rank\": 0.005015985002349619, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reallocation ceremony\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3436}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3460}, {\"ngram\": \"the occasion\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3517}, {\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's special, and my son will be able to witness that so that's a moment that I will be very happy for.\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my son\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3561}, {\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will be able to see mommy collect that bronze medal - even though it's 12 years later - but I am still super happy for that,\\\" Carter said.\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3770, \"end\": 3776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9950010684583732, \"rank\": 0.005015985002349619, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mommy\", \"from\": 3664, \"to\": 3669}, {\"ngram\": \"that bronze medal\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carter, who has officially retired, ends her chapter with a personal best of 52.79, which makes her the second-fastest Jamaican behind Melaine Walker (52.42) and the 12th-fastest woman in the world in history.\", \"from\": 3784, \"to\": 3993, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3784, \"end\": 3790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9950010684583732, \"rank\": 0.005015985002349619, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}, {\"begin\": 3919, \"end\": 3926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melaine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Melaine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melaine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melaine\"}, {\"begin\": 3927, \"end\": 3933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kemba_Walker\", \"score\": 0.9999999983506314, \"rank\": 1.6492761974250634e-09, \"text\": \"Walker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kemba_Walker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kemba_Walker\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her chapter\", \"from\": 3825, \"to\": 3836}, {\"ngram\": \"the 12th-fastest woman\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 3968}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 3981}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 3992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is also only the third Jamaican to medal in the event at the Olympic Games, following in the strides of Deon Hemmings who won gold in 1996 (Atlanta) and silver in 2000 (Sydney); and Walker who took gold at the 2008 Games in Beijing.\", \"from\": 3995, \"to\": 4231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4022, \"end\": 4030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999987273494211, \"rank\": 1.272652180024198e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 4103, \"end\": 4116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deon_Hemmings\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Deon Hemmings\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deon_Hemmings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deon_Hemmings\"}, {\"begin\": 4139, \"end\": 4146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999999759779715, \"rank\": 1.910280990166273e-08, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}, {\"begin\": 4168, \"end\": 4174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9997831678885148, \"rank\": 0.0002078660390364806, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q4